Enum Class InformationSupplyChain

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<InformationSupplyChain>
org.odpi.openmetadata.samples.archiveutilities.businesssystems.InformationSupplyChain
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<InformationSupplyChain>, Constable
public enum InformationSupplyChain extends Enum<InformationSupplyChain>
A description of the predefined information supply chains. There are two formats - one for templates and the other for normal information supply chains.
